Text.SourceString: My name?// Hmm… My name’s <NPCName>Oliver</>. Why?
Um, yeah! This is a normal day on the island, I guess.//Except now you’re here.
My dad says if I promise to do my reading after dinner, I’m allowed to play at the beach after school…
Yeah, I can watch TV… Of course.
Dad and <NPCName>Jim</> used to chase monster fish!//<portrait=normal>And listen, listen… Dad was on TV a couple of times, being interviewed.//<portrait=happy>How cool is that?!
Being a farmer is cool too. I hope you get to be on TV sometime.
I wanna be a policeman when I grow up and chase bad guys!
There are no bad guys here, so I’ll have to go somewhere else.
I really like all my friends here… They’re never mean to me.
We get to look for bugs and dig worms together. Oh, don’t worry. We don’t take them with us.//Only look at them!
I’m so excited for the weekend! I’m going to play at the beach all weekend long!
Oh! Or I might go to the park and play with <NPCName>Taco</>. If I’m lucky, I might get to play with <NPCName>Peanut</> and <NPCName>Butter</>, too.
It’s Friday! Yippee!
I’m so excited for the weekend! I’m going to play at the beach all day tomorrow!
Oh! Or I might go to the park and play with <NPCName>Taco</>. If I’m lucky, I might get to play with <NPCName>Peanut</> and <NPCName>Butter</>, too.
Dad and <NPCName>Jim</> used to chase monster fish!//<portrait=normal>And listen, listen… Dad was on TV a couple of times, being interviewed.//<portrait=happy>How cool is that?!
Being a farmer is cool too. I hope you get to be on TV sometime.
I wanna be a policeman when I grow up and chase bad guys!
There are no bad guys here, so I’ll have to go somewhere else.
Usually, on Sundays, <NPCName>Valentina</> gets a visit from her uncle. So we can’t hang out too long.
But sometimes, he plays volleyball with us… <NPCName>Rafael</>, his name is.//He’s not very good at it, but he’s a lot of fun!
Surfing is super fun! Oh, but… I can’t wait to dive.//I’m gonna dive too when I’m a little older.
School was good yesterday. I learned a lot!
Errr… I can’t remember right now. I can tell you what we learned today, though.
When I get bored on the weekend, I go to Hillside and play with <NPCName>Taco</>.//<portrait=normal>But only after I do my reading homework.
Oh, <NPCName>Taco</> the dog.//The one wearing a fancy scarf!
When I get bored on the weekend, I go to Hillside and play with <NPCName>Taco</>.//<portrait=normal>But only after I do my reading homework.
Oh, <NPCName>Taco</> the dog.//The one wearing a fancy scarf!
Seafood ramen is the best kind of ramen.//It’s like the sea, with bits of shrimp and clams, but you can eat them.
Mr. <NPCName>Barnes</> said I’ll need to train in Pokyo to become a policeman because they don’t have the academy here.
But for now, my job is to study hard and eat a lot of greens.//<portrait=normal>So I can grow big and strong someday.
Dad told me I could be whatever I want if I put my heart in it.
What did you want to be when you grew up?
Whoa! Your dream came true!
Well, you’re rich now. You have a farm and all… Are you happy?
Whoa! That sounds so cool!
Sometimes I go to the library on the weekend to check out some books.//<NPCName>Millie</> lets me have first dibs when they get the new Detective Foyle graphic novels.
You have to be healthy and strong if you want to pass the police exam.//I’m eating my vegetables and protein, so I think I will be.
There must be a lot of bugs and worms at your farm, huh?
I try to have as much fun as possible on the weekend… That way, when I’m at school, I don’t feel left out.
Reading at the library is so much better than at home. Because sometimes Dad or <NPCName>Jim</> laughs so hard, the whole house shakes.
Oh, um… Never <NPCName>Jim</>. He doesn’t laugh very much, actually.
Reading at the library is so much better than at home. Because sometimes Dad or <NPCName>Jim</> laughs so hard, the whole house shakes.
Oh, um… Never <NPCName>Jim</>. He doesn’t laugh very much, actually.
I wanna see Pokyo when I grow up. You’re from there, right?
Dad said I’m a Pokyoite too.//<portrait=normal>He and Mom adopted me there and brought me here when I was a baby.
It’s Taco Tuesday! I didn’t bring lunch on purpose today.
We used to play at your farm after school to try to see ghosts.//We wanted to see if it was haunted.
Oh, don’t worry! We never found anything funny.//<portrait=normal>So you can rest peacefully.
I can’t wait for the weekend to play mini golf. It’s a fun game to play alone.
My favorite dinosaurs are velociraptors.//<portrait=happy>They’re the smartest kind, you know!//<portrait=doubt>Err… I’m pretty sure.
Do you fly kites, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Dad says I need to take school seriously but also never miss playtime.//He says having hobbies is just as important.
I wanna see Pokyo when I grow up. You’re from there, right?
Dad said I’m a Pokyoite too.//<portrait=normal>He and Mom adopted me there and brought me here when I was a baby.
My favorite dinosaurs are velociraptors.//<portrait=happy>They’re the smartest kind, you know!//<portrait=doubt>Err… I’m pretty sure.
We used to play at your farm after school to try to see ghosts.//We wanted to see if it was haunted.
Oh, don’t worry! We never found anything funny.//<portrait=normal>So you can rest peacefully.
Dad says I need to take school seriously but also never miss playtime.//He says having hobbies is just as important.
There was a scientist who moved here last year.//<portrait=normal>He’s at the beach a lot… I think his name is <NPCName>Surya</>.
He came to the school and introduced himself.//<portrait=doubt>He told us his name meant “the sun” in Indonesian.//<portrait=normal>Is he your friend?
Will you be planting any flowers this Spring? I can’t plant too much because we live on the beach. The sand won’t work.
But even if I had land, I probably wouldn’t plant anything. I don’t like gardening.
We learned flowers and bee houses can help increase the bee population.
Do you have one of those bee houses at your farm?
I learned at school that farmers are usually working at their farms. But I see you around a lot!
I guess you’re a different kind of farmer, huh?
I learned at school that farmers are usually working at their farms. But I see you around a lot!
I guess you’re a different kind of farmer, huh?
I think it’s a good day to have ice cream!
You’re right! Every day is a good day to have ice cream!
Me and my friends will be there for beach cleanup! We’re super excited.
We get to play at the beach the whole day, and win prizes.
It seems like a good day to have ice cream!
You’re right. Every day is a good day to have ice cream.//But Dad always says not too much of it, or I’ll get a stomachache.
I can’t wait to build a snowman with my friends!
Yippee!
It seems like a good day to have ice cream!
You’re right. Every day is a good day to have ice cream.//But Dad always says not too much of it, or I’ll get a stomachache.
Ice cream is the perfect treat. You can eat it in Spring...Fall like now, even Winter.//It's NEVER too cold for ice cream...or too hot! That's just silly.
I hope Dad cooks seafood ramen tonight.//<portrait=happy>Yummy!
I don’t think bees are flying around during Winter.
It might be too cold for them.
I want to make the biggest snowman in the world! But I don’t think we have enough snow yet.
It’s easy. When I have enough money, I’m going to order snow from Socket Electronics and bring it here.
Aww… Winter’s ending soon. I’m gonna miss the snow.
Oh well! At least I get to see frogs soon!
Umm… Excuse me, <PlayerName>$honorifics $player</>, but what do you do all Winter?
Do you still farm?
Oh noooo! Can’t do anything today.
Dad won’t let me out. He said I’ll get sick if I play in the rain.
I’ve been inside all day. It’s so boring.
I wanna go out and find a puddle.
They keep playing the same shows on TV lately… I think they ran out of ideas.
I like the rain. I’d just like it better if I got to play in it a bit longer.
Dad said I have to go home right away after school.
I have to finish this chapter today.
Mr. <NPCName>Barnes</> told me if I missed a reading assignment again, I might have to stay after school for detention.
I wish I could read my graphic novels instead. But I’m almost done, so no big deal. Humph.
Oh, he said we all have to read the same book so we can talk about it as a group.
It’s snowing today! I hope we can get off school early so I can build a snowman in the park.
We learned about early civilizations… Errr… About how they lived and what tools they used back then.
I have to finish this chapter today.
Mr. <NPCName>Barnes</> told me if I missed a reading assignment again, I might have to stay after school for detention.
Look at my footprints! Snow is so much fun.
Wow! Look at yours! They’re like a giant’s.
I have a pet, but lizards are very shy, you know. It won’t come out when anyone is around.//It only comes out when the house is really quiet.
Hmm… Where’s the remote? Is it behind you?
Let me see… Can you move a bit?
Dinner was so yummy! I’m stuffed… But maybe I can have another plate.
Umm… Maybe not. I don’t want my stomach to hurt.
Eww… I just sat on something slimy! What is that?
Oh, yikes… I don’t want to look.
I’m going to play at the beach after school.
I’m allowed to play after school, but only until dinnertime. It’s okay. That’s enough!
My favorite subject is science. What was your favorite subject in school?
I had a lot of fun.//Science helps you solve cases, you know! It's super cool.
School must be very different from what you had back then.
Are you looking for Mr. <NPCName>Barnes</>?
I hope Dad’s making smoked salmon tonight.//I’m starving!
School makes me really hungry.
I gotta get my homework done fast tonight. Boy Detective is on TV!
My homework was really hard last night.//<portrait=doubt>I had to ask Dad for help.
Dad knows everything. He’s really smart.
Do you ever eat fish for dinner, <PlayerName>$player</>?
There’s lots of fish around the island. I want to taste them all.
Dad keeps talking about something called the starboard of a boat.//Is that like the stars in the sky?
I wonder if there are more boats in the world than stars.//I’ll ask Dad.
It’s kinda boring on the island sometimes.//I wish there was a mystery for me to solve, like in Boy Detective.
Dad says it’s not nice to wish for people to be murdered.
Dad says his favorite day is Friday. He says mine might be Friday when I grow up, too.
I didn’t do so well on my homework last week.//I don’t really get math.
Dad says I have to learn math if I want to be a detective, though.//<portrait=normal>Guess I gotta keep working on it.
Do you have any animals on your farm, <PlayerName>$player</>? Can I come pet them sometime?
I’ve never seen a cow up close before.
Have you ever solved a mystery? I bet it’s really fun.
I can’t wait to solve mysteries when I grow up.
I wonder what we’re doing in school tomorrow. Mr. <NPCName>Barnes</> always tells us about interesting stuff.
Have you ever had <NPCName>Jim</>’s smoked salmon? It’s really good!
Sometimes he brings some when he comes over to play chess with Dad.
I have a big test tomorrow. Excuse me, <PlayerName>$player</>, but I have to get back to studying.
That’s what Dad told me to say when I need to work.
It’s kinda boring on the island sometimes.//I wish there was a mystery for me to solve, like in Boy Detective.
Dad says it’s not nice to wish for people to be murdered.
Do you know anything about Pokyo?
Dad says we can go to the beach tomorrow since it’s a weekend. Yay!
Got any ice cream, <PlayerName>$player</>? I’m starving!
I gotta get my homework done fast tonight. Boy Detective is coming on TV again!
I didn’t do so well on my homework last week. I don’t really get math.
Dad says I have to learn math if I want to be a detective, though. Guess I gotta keep working on it.
I’m glad I got to sleep in today. Getting up every morning to go to school is hard.
If you need any coconut drinks or fish stuff, you should go to the Beach Shack!
Dad says he doesn’t need to pay for advertising with me around. But I don’t know what that means.
I wonder what we’re doing in school tomorrow. Mr. <NPCName>Barnes</> always tells us about interesting stuff.
Dad got me this really cool kite for my birthday. It looks like a big fish.//I like to fly it in the park when it’s windy.
I don’t wanna go to school tomorrow. I’m tired of taking tests.
Were you really good at school, <PlayerName>$player</>? I think Dad was.
It’s okay if you weren’t. I’m not very good at it, either.
I’m so hungry! Is it time for dinner yet?
Dad got me a new action figure when he went into town the other day. It’s really cool.//See? The arms go up and down, and it says a bunch of stuff.
I wonder what Pokyo looks like. Dad says it’s a big city with lots of people and lots of noise.
I wonder if there’s places to go fishing there.
It’s the last day of school for this week! Yay!
What’s your favorite kind of ice cream? I really like mint.//It feels <Italic>windy</>in my mouth. You should try it!
Dad caught some really big fish a long time ago. He said he started fishing when he was my age.
I wish he would teach me to fish.
<NPCName>Valentina</> says even after we finish school here, we have to go to school somewhere else and get a degree. What’s that?
I don’t wanna go to school forever.
I stepped on a can at the beach the other day, and it made my foot bleed.//It really hurt, but Dad put a bandage on and it felt better.
There sure is a lot of garbage in the ocean. I wonder how it got there.
It’s almost time for school exams.//I hope I’m ready.
I’ve been studying really hard, but it seems like everyone else gets it better than I do.//Guess I gotta keep working.
I wish the ocean would warm up faster so I can go swimming. It’s still cold from Winter.
I wonder what Dad’s gonna get me for my birthday. I hope it’s the new Boy Detective shirt!
Have you seen anything strange on the island, <PlayerName>$player</>? Any mysteries to solve?
No? Oh, okay.
Dad says all the big fish come out in Summer. I wonder where they hide during Winter.
The Beach Shack is sooooo busy in Summer. Where do all those people come from?
Do they live in the ocean and come out just to buy ice cream?
Why is it so hot? I hope Dad has some extra ice cream.
I don’t wanna go to school when it’s this hot. It’s too icky.
Dad says I should play with some kids from my class, but I don’t wanna.//<portrait=happy>I like to play alone sometimes.
Dad says Fall is salmon season. I hope <NPCName>Jim</> makes some more smoked salmon!
Hmm...was it Fall or Summer?//I can't remember.
It’s kinda cold out here, but the ocean is still warm. How does that work?
Can I still go surfing?
Did you give your animals a hug today? You should make sure they’re happy.
It’s fun to jump in big piles of leaves.//<portrait=normal>You can make them spray everywhere like—
Dad says farmers harvest a lot of crops in Fall. Did you harvest anything?
Can you cook anything tasty with those veggies?
No one comes to the Beach Shack when it’s cold outside.
I guess that’s because no one goes to the beach when it’s cold outside.
Eating ice cream makes me feel even colder in Winter.//Brrrr!
Is it time for the Winter Market yet? Dad always buys me a new toy!
I’m tired of wearing a jacket every day. Is it time for Summer yet?
I don’t like standing in the rain. It’s too wet.
I wish Dad had gotten me the Boy Detective umbrella for my birthday.
Rain, rain, go away! I wanna go out and play.
It’s dark and wet and cold out here.//I wish I was at home.
Guess I can’t play outside today.
That’s okay. Boy Detective is coming on TV tonight.
I always sleep better when it’s raining out.
I’m getting kinda sleepy now…zzz…
I think Dad fell asleep on the sofa again. He always does that when the TV’s on.
I hope it doesn’t rain again tomorrow. I wanna go to the beach.
I don’t wanna go out when there’s thunder! It’s too scary!
<PlayerName>$player</>, I d-don’t really w-wanna t-talk right now. C-can we do it l-later?
Yikes! Thunder!
It’s scary out here. I wanna go home!
The storm makes everything creepy. You can’t even see anything in the rain.
Why is thunder so big and loud? It sounds like a giant foot stomping on Coral Island.
I wanna go to sleep, but the thunder is keeping me awake.
I’m gonna be sleepy tomorrow…
SNOW DAY!
I think I’ll read inside while it snows.
You can’t really grow any plants when it’s like this, right? It would make them cold and sad.
Look at it snow out there! Is it gonna snow forever?
I hope so.
I wonder what fish think of snow. Do they even know it’s there?
[<NPCName>Oliver </> looks busy studying.]
Sorry, <PlayerName>$player</>, but I gotta pay attention.
Dad has lots of books about fishing in here. I don’t really understand most of them.
If you catch a fish, you should show it to my dad. He knows a lot about them.
The wind feels nice.//<portrait=annoyed>But don't open your mouth so wide...sands might go in.
Dad always makes a big deal out of me getting lots of fresh air. He says it’s good for kids like me.
What does he mean? Is it not good for every kid?//Like, is fresh air bad for <NPCName>Valentina</> or something?
The sky is so big! Sometimes I just look up and stare at it.
I hope it doesn’t mind me staring.
Mini golf is hard! The clubs are <Italic>really</> heavy.
Mom said that kindness is cool.//I wanna be kind so I can be cool.
I am?! Thank you!//You're very kind, <PlayerName>$player</>.//That makes you very cool!
